skillType.name: Wall
skillType.desc: Defensive - Absorbs damage dealt to the Commander and subtracts from own health

skillType.name: Evade
skillType.desc: Defensive - 50% chance to negate the effects of an enemy Activation skill on this

skillType.name: Payback
skillType.desc: Defensive - When enemy uses an Activation skill on this (Other than Mimic), 50% chance to use same skill on the original enemy unit

skillType.name: Flying
skillType.desc: Defensive - 50% chance to dodge attacks by non-Flying units

skillType.name: Armored
skillType.desc: Defensive - Reduces damage taken by attacks

skillType.name: Counter
skillType.desc: Defensive - When damaged by an attack, deal damage back to attacker

skillType.name: Regenerate
skillType.desc: Defensive - When card health reaches zero, 50% chance of gaining back health

skillType.name: Heal
skillType.desc: Activation - Increases health of a random allied Assault card

skillType.name: Rally
skillType.desc: Activation - Increases the Attack of a random allied Assault card

skillType.name: Enfeeble
skillType.desc: Activation - Increases any damage directed at a random enemy Assault card

skillType.name: Strike
skillType.desc: Activation - Deals damage to a random enemy Assault card

skillType.name: Jam
skillType.desc: Activation - 50% chance of preventing a random enemy Assault card from attacking or using Activation skills next turn.

skillType.name: Weaken
skillType.desc: Activation - Reduce the attack of a random enemy Assault card

skillType.name: Siege
skillType.desc: Activation - Deals damage to a random enemy Structure

skillType.name: Mimic
skillType.desc: Activation - Uses any "Activation" skills of an enemy Assault card, except Mimic. Ignores Faction modifiers (ex. "Strike Raider 1" becomes "Strike 1")

skillType.name: Flurry
skillType.desc: Combat-Modifier - 50% chance to Attack extra times a turn

skillType.name: Swipe
skillType.desc: Combat-Modifier - When attacking an Assault unit this also attacks the adjacent enemy Assault units, if any

skillType.name: Fear
skillType.desc: Combat-Modifier - Attack Commander directly

skillType.name: AntiAir
skillType.desc: Combat-Modifier - Always hits flying units and deals extra damage to them

skillType.name: Valor
skillType.desc: Combat-Modifier - When enemy has more Assault units than you, deal additional attack damage

skillType.name: Pierce
skillType.desc: Combat-Modifier - Reduces the effect of enemy skills that prevent Attack Damage

skillType.name: Pierce
skillType.desc: Combat-Modifier - Reduces the effect of enemy skills that prevent Attack Damage

skillType.name: Immobilize
skillType.desc: Damage-Dependent - After damaging an enemy from an attack, 50% chance of preventing damaged Assault card from attacking

skillType.name: Poison
skillType.desc: Damage-Dependent - Assault cards that took attack damage from this unit take damage at the beginning of the poisoned unit's turn

skillType.name: Crush
skillType.desc: Damage-Dependent - Damages the enemy Commander when the card destroys an enemy Assault card by attack damage

skillType.name: Leech
skillType.desc: Damage-Dependent - Heals this card as it deals attack damage to an Assault card

skillType.name: Siphon
skillType.desc: Damage-Dependent - Heals the Commander as this card deals attack damage to an Assault card

skillType.name: Rush
skillType.desc: Activation - Decrease the cost of a random owner's Assault card

skillType.name: Augment
skillType.desc: Activation - Increase the effectiveness of a unit's Activation skills, other than Augment (example using Augment 1: Strike 1 = Strike 2)

skillType.name: Blitz
skillType.desc: Triggered - When played, if assault unit directly across from this has 0 cooldown, take an action this turn. (Use Activation skills and attack, still takes action in regular order)

skillType.name: Repair
skillType.desc: Activation - Replenish a Structure's lost health.

skillType.name: Split
skillType.desc: Activation - Make a copy of this (Cannot be Mimiced!)

skillType.name: Backfire
skillType.desc: Destroyed - When this is destroyed, deal damage to own Commander

skillType.name: Shock
skillType.desc: Activation - Deal damage directly to the Enemy Commander (Damage does not redirect to Walls)

skillType.name: Recharge
skillType.desc: Activation - 50% chance that this card will return to the bottom of the deck after use

skillType.name: Infuse
skillType.desc: Activation - Change the type of any Assault unit (allied or enemy) Also changes any helpful skill (Heal, Rally, etc.) that only affects a certain type to affect the specified type. (Infuse status cannot be Cleansed)

skillType.name: Fusion
skillType.desc: Static - When 3 or more cards with Fusion are active, double the effects of this card's skills.

skillType.name: Mist
skillType.desc: Static - Allied Assault and Structure cards are hidden until active or destroyed

skillType.name: Protect
skillType.desc: Activation - Prevents damage from attack or any skill

skillType.name: Berserk
skillType.desc: Damage-Dependent - When this unit deals attack damage, permanently raise Attack

skillType.name: Supply
skillType.desc: Activation - Heal this unit and adjacent Assault units (Can only be Mimiced by Assault units)

skillType.name: Tribute
skillType.desc: Defensive - When another allied assault card, uses an Activation Skill on this (besides skills affected by Chaos), 50% chance to use that ability on the original unit.

skillType.name: Chaos
skillType.desc: Activation - If an enemy Assault unit were to use an Activation skill that would target one of its enemies, it targets an ally or itself instead. (The skills used by a Chaosed unit cannot be Evaded)

skillType.name: Refresh
skillType.desc: Defensive - At the end of this unit's turn, restore all health to full.

skillType.name: Cleanse
skillType.desc: Activation - Remove all negative status effects from an ally Assault unit (Poison, Disease, Jam, Immobilize, Enfeeble, Chaos, Freeze, Stun).

skillType.name: Disease
skillType.desc: Damage-Dependent - After damaging an enemy from an attack, damaged Assault unit can no longer regain lost health.

skillType.name: Freeze
skillType.desc: Activation - Prevents enemy assault unit from taking an action or decreasing its timer.

skillType.name: Blizzard
skillType.desc: Static - Allied Assault and Structure cards are hidden until active or destroyed

skillType.name: Intercept
skillType.desc: Defensive - If an adjacent Assault unit were to be the target of an Enemy skill while this unit is not the target of the same skill, target this unit instead if this unit is a valid target. (Only 1 Intercept per skill. If two possible Intercepts, oldest unit has priority.)

skillType.name: Burst
skillType.desc: Combat-Modifier - When this unit attacks, if the defending Assault unit's health is at max, this unit deals additional attack damage.

skillType.name: Summon
skillType.desc: Activation - Plays a copy of the specified card.

skillType.name: Emulate
skillType.desc: Defensive - When an opponent's card uses a non-chaosed Activation skill that targets the Assault card opposite of this, copy the effect for this card.

skillType.name: Legion
skillType.desc: Triggered - On your turn, before cards take Actions (After you play a card if able) increase the attack and health of this card for each adjacent card of the same faction.

skillType.name: Stun
skillType.desc: Defensive - Any Assault unit that damages this from an attack becomes stunned. Stunned units cannot attack until after their next turn.

skillType.name: Sunder
skillType.desc: Damage-Dependent - After damaging an enemy from an attack, damaged Assault unit can no longer gain additional attack (if attack is lowered from base amount, it is still reset to base normally).

skillType.name: Phase
skillType.desc: Damage-Dependant - When this deals attack damage to an assault card, the damaged card can't be targeted by friendly activation skills on its next turn (including cleanse)

skillType.name: Freeze
skillType.desc: Activation - Prevents enemy assault unit from taking an action or decreasing its timer.
